	**************************************************
	*						 *
	*	       2.1 SERIES NEWS			 *
	*						 *
	**************************************************


		CHANGES IN R VERSION 2.1.3


BUG FIXES

    o	Corrected app-defaults file to match settings for SuperCurve 1.5.


		CHANGES IN R VERSION 2.1.2


NEW FEATURES

    o	No code changes. Unnecessary version change attempting to trigger
	package rebuild on R-Forge -- any commit triggers rebuild, checked
	every 4 hours.


		CHANGES IN R VERSION 2.1.1


BUG FIXES

    o	Removed quantification file preflight error checking code.


		CHANGES IN R VERSION 2.1.0


SIGNIFICANT USER-VISIBLE CHANGES

    o	Normalization method can now be selected.

    o	Added support for ArrayPro quantification files.

NEW FEATURES

    o	Changes necessary to support SuperCurve 1.5.


	**************************************************
	*						 *
	*	       2.0 SERIES NEWS			 *
	*						 *
	**************************************************


		CHANGES IN R VERSION 2.0.2


NEW FEATURES

    o	Added SVN revision information to most of the package files.

    o	Added COPYRIGHTS file.


		CHANGES IN R VERSION 2.0.1


NEW FEATURES

    o	Each analysis performed will be logged in its own logfile.


BUG FIXES

    o	Workaround for issue where occasionally tabs would be missing
	from the user interface.

    o	Fixed minor issue with console diversions not shutting down
	after each analysis.


		CHANGES IN R VERSION 2.0.0


SIGNIFICANT USER-VISIBLE CHANGES

    o	Completely redesigned tabbed user interface.

    o	Settings from previous run can now be trivially
	reloaded, possibly tweaked, and rerun.

    o	Progress is monitored such that user can tell what
	stage the SuperCurve processing is currently at
	and what slide is being handled.


	**************************************************
	*						 *
	*	       1.0 SERIES NEWS			 *
	*						 *
	**************************************************


		CHANGES IN R VERSION 1.0.1


NEW FEATURES

    o	Added sc() as alias for supercurveGUI() for backwards
	compatibility.


		CHANGES IN R VERSION 1.0.0


NEW FEATURES

    o	Creation of package so that Tcl/Tk requirement would not affect
	people who only wish to use package SuperCurve without the GUI.

    o	Renamed sc() as supercurveGUI().

    o	Added filters to file selection dialogs.


BUG FIXES

    o	Changed output directory selection dialog to not require an
	existing file, avoiding first-use "chicken & egg" scenario.

    o	Added appropriate dialog titles where necessary.

